{"tid":1652773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(新職業）和理幫拖師","createTime":"2019-10-13T19:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T20:10:34.000Z","uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"74fdd7fc7dd0538f75ab6187836ff4271158f35b","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:51:37.000Z","msg":"睇見卧底狗問題嚴重，加上多區開花令和勇及支援分配出現不均衡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以希望和理手足務必進化至幫拖師。見到手足被1至2隻狗 (猶其便衣狗) 壓在地上時，盡量小心地走到狗隻的盲眼位 ,一巴<span style=\"color: red;\">車</span>落去隻狗耳度 (咁當然係喺佢發現你之前同埋男手足效果更佳) ，按照常理狗隻會應聲倒地，頓時感到耳嗚，失去5成攻擊力。<br />\n<br />\n同時眾幫拖師應馬上即場吹雞及繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">車</span>直至救回手足並極速散水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地如果唔每人做多一步既話就唔會衝得過lee個瓶頸。見到多區手足被4人甚至1人狗小隊壓在地上，同時附近經過的人都只報以<br />\n冷眼。<br />\n<br />\n並非叫大家主動打狗，可能香港人被欺壓已久，情緒智商奇高。但此言絕非讚美，只是對大家在是與非之間的界線感到不解。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都可以為被拘捕的手足繼續支持下去，運動不能停濟不前。<br />\n<br />\n最後<span style=\"color: blue;\">水能載舟 亦能覆舟</span>。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5af3e1b0b161efcf8b99e15a56705833bfb321f","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:53:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c07ac8bc78f3cdcc5a9233945f9a474ffb2ab374","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:03:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e148873aae99b79227b1e648076c6421bb1bdff","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:03:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"895bdf80767b14337018e2542b8947a8419f9224","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:04:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c2fe093eb79c3f3f848a23709fa589d1d3b4ca1","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:04:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66676e6d163c11ccb8ec366348a097a4e9fc3a6e","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:04:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1798051dbb4cf6b7e35c8f008179a1f4eb9bfcec","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:04:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0f4af99c2c729e369f3242124a9e9848681ee145","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:04:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e6c3c07b49c98d7a04a916118f9965face3686a","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:05:19.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"14a20174fe1241685e9ef7588a1043cf7ff91040","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84af89d1a871c4ffe75489ca2b1ac3ee4f6c8cf5","tid":1652773,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:10:34.000Z","msg":"訓哂diu"}]}